# No environment variables are required for the interactive map (WO-003).
# react-leaflet uses OpenStreetMap/CartoDB Positron tiles which are free and key-free.
#
# Code Connect (publish .figma.tsx mappings to Figma Dev Mode):
# FIGMA_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_figma_personal_access_token
#
# Add future API keys here as needed, e.g.:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPS_API_KEY=your_key_here
